<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 08:10:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对决策的厌恶阻碍了与哈马斯的人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/decision-averse-netanyahu-is-deliberately-holding-up-a-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018e-c480-d6f4-afaf-ecc286050000</link><description>哈马斯并不是开罗谈判中唯一拖延时间的一方。以色列总理似乎知道达成协议的代价可能是其联盟的终结，他与那些想要拒绝美国妥协的人站在一起，很可能将谈判引向死胡同</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/decision-averse-netanyahu-is-deliberately-holding-up-a-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018e-c480-d6f4-afaf-ecc286050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级部长考虑投票反对不包括所有人质的停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-ministers-will-vote-against-cease-fire-deal-that-does-not-include-all-hostages/0000018e-c4c5-dc93-adce-eef5e11b0000</link><description>内阁高级成员认为，这将是与哈马斯的最后一项以人质换取休战的协议，未来几轮谈判几乎是不可能的。据接近内塔尼亚胡的消息人士称，宗教犹太复国主义和奥兹玛·耶胡迪特部长将反对当前协议，但不会推翻联盟</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/top-israeli-ministers-will-vote-against-cease-fire-deal-that-does-not-include-all-hostages/0000018e-c4c5-dc93-adce-eef5e11b0000</guid></item><item><title>最高指挥官遇刺后紧张局势加剧，以色列和伊朗相互威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article-live/biden-slams-netanyahus-handling-of-gaza-campaign-war-cabinet-discusses-truce-talks/0000018e-c5c4-dfe9-a19f-f5e59fb70000</link><description>美国称哈马斯尚未对提议作出回应 ■ 以色列国防军表示，从汗尤尼斯撤军将导致拉法发生战斗 ■ 以色列国防部长告诉美国国防部长，尚未确定发起拉法攻势的日期 ■ 《华尔街日报》：美国人质协议提议包括将 15 万巴勒斯坦人送回以色列加沙北部</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 02:19:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article-live/biden-slams-netanyahus-handling-of-gaza-campaign-war-cabinet-discusses-truce-talks/0000018e-c5c4-dfe9-a19f-f5e59fb70000</guid></item><item><title>拜登猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡处理加沙战争的方式：“他的做法是错误的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-slams-netanyahus-handling-of-gaza-war-what-hes-doing-is-a-mistake/0000018e-c507-d6f4-afaf-ed47502c0000</link><description>美国总统在就美国支持以色列战争努力发出迄今为止最明确的最后通牒一周后发表此番言论</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 22:56:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-slams-netanyahus-handling-of-gaza-war-what-hes-doing-is-a-mistake/0000018e-c507-d6f4-afaf-ed47502c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡浪费了以色列的国际信誉，现在他正在争取时间</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-frittered-away-israels-international-credit-and-now-hes-playing-for-time/0000018e-c4cc-dc93-adce-eefc6ef30000</link><description>由于以色列总理拒绝做出重大决定，只有他的联盟伙伴才能结束“比比时代”。是民族团结党领导的脱欧协议阵营，还是希望内塔尼亚胡向他们承诺的“全面胜利”的斯莫特里奇和本格维尔？</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 22:13:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-frittered-away-israels-international-credit-and-now-hes-playing-for-time/0000018e-c4cc-dc93-adce-eefc6ef30000</guid></item><item><title>针对俄亥俄州立大学未能解决犹太学生骚扰问题的投诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/complaint-filed-against-ohio-state-for-failing-to-address-harassment-of-jewish-students/0000018e-c4b1-dc93-adce-eef14d8e0000</link><description>投诉敦促教育部迫使俄亥俄州立大学采取措施保障犹太和以色列学生的安全，并向教职员工、学生和工作人员提供强制性反犹太主义培训</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 21:21:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-10/ty-article/.premium/complaint-filed-against-ohio-state-for-failing-to-address-harassment-of-jewish-students/0000018e-c4b1-dc93-adce-eef14d8e0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示内塔尼亚胡在选举中惨败。但还有什么可以拯救他呢？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/polls-show-netanyahu-crashing-to-defeat-in-elections-but-what-could-still-save-him/0000018e-c3f7-d480-a99e-cff7c1980000</link><description>以色列人会投票让总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡下台吗？这取决于下次选举的内容、选举时间以及加沙战争和哈马斯仍扣押人质的情况</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 20:43:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/polls-show-netanyahu-crashing-to-defeat-in-elections-but-what-could-still-save-him/0000018e-c3f7-d480-a99e-cff7c1980000</guid></item><item><title>获释的以色列人质哀叹缺乏国家财政援助、官僚僵局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-lament-lack-of-aid-from-the-state-bureaucratic-deadlock/0000018e-c477-d1b7-a3af-e77f601f0000</link><description>一名获释人质告诉立法者，她得到的只是每月 1,350 谢克尔（365 美元）的战俘津贴。 “他们既不是恐怖活动的受害者，也不是被释放的战俘，”一名获释人质的母亲说。 “他们是穿着睡衣从床上被绑架的人”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 20:31:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/freed-israeli-hostages-lament-lack-of-aid-from-the-state-bureaucratic-deadlock/0000018e-c477-d1b7-a3af-e77f601f0000</guid></item><item><title>男子在拿撒勒家中枪杀家人后自杀；三人死亡，两人重伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/man-shoots-family-in-nazareth-home-commits-suicide-three-killed-two-severely-injure/0000018e-c45d-d6f4-afaf-ec5f93320000</link><description>据邻居称，枪手今年 34 岁，因继承问题与母亲发生争执，被邻居视为问题人物。警方称枪手在杀死三名亲属并打伤另一名亲属后自杀</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 20:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/man-shoots-family-in-nazareth-home-commits-suicide-three-killed-two-severely-injure/0000018e-c45d-d6f4-afaf-ec5f93320000</guid></item><item><title>尽管内塔尼亚胡声称，以色列国防部长告诉美国没有确定拉法进攻的日期</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/despite-netanyahus-claim-gallant-tells-u-s-that-no-date-set-for-rafah-offensive/0000018e-c43f-d1b7-a3af-e73fb6ab0000</link><description>拜登的国家安全顾问表示，美国“仍然没有看到可靠且可执行的计划来解决以色列从拉法撤离和平民护理问题”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 20:02:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/despite-netanyahus-claim-gallant-tells-u-s-that-no-date-set-for-rafah-offensive/0000018e-c43f-d1b7-a3af-e73fb6ab0000</guid></item><item><title>“美国对以色列的军事援助受到威胁。更多人会说应该砍掉”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-04-09/ty-article-podcast/u-s-military-aid-to-israel-is-endangered-more-people-will-say-it-should-be-cut/0000018e-c310-d6f4-afaf-ef526e160000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 19:22:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-04-09/ty-article-podcast/u-s-military-aid-to-israel-is-endangered-more-people-will-say-it-should-be-cut/0000018e-c310-d6f4-afaf-ef526e160000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全内阁在极右翼部长的压力下讨论人质交易进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/security-cabinet-set-to-discuss-gaza-truce-progress-due-to-far-right-ministers-pressure/0000018e-c31f-d480-a99e-cf5ff2030000</link><description>极右翼部长本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇展示了他们的联盟力量，要求参与有关战争未来的决策过程，尽管他们担心信息会泄露并在这个敏感时刻破坏谈判</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 18:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/security-cabinet-set-to-discuss-gaza-truce-progress-due-to-far-right-ministers-pressure/0000018e-c31f-d480-a99e-cf5ff2030000</guid></item><item><title>碾压反政府抗议者的以色列司机因警方上诉被接受而被拘留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-driver-who-ran-over-protesters-to-stay-in-custody-as-police-appeal-accepted/0000018e-c3c2-dc93-adce-eff23a150000</link><description>法官没有发现任何迹象表明司机在撞倒反政府抗议者之前试图刹车。法官写道：“他表现出对人命的深深蔑视和巨大的危险。”他可能面临20年以上监禁</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 18:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-driver-who-ran-over-protesters-to-stay-in-custody-as-police-appeal-accepted/0000018e-c3c2-dc93-adce-eff23a150000</guid></item><item><title>“我来自美国，婊子”：美国直播主播约翰尼·索马里因涉嫌骚扰女警察而在以色列被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-livestreamer-johnny-somali-arrested-in-israel-on-suspicion-of-harassing-policewoman/0000018e-c380-dc93-adce-eff0f9720000</link><description>约翰尼·索马里在特拉维夫的一次抗议活动中被捕并被释放，随后因警方发现一段他对女警察使用粗俗语言的在线视频而再次被捕。索马里称自己被捕是“假新闻”，他面临听证会，可能会被驱逐出境</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 17:57:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/u-s-livestreamer-johnny-somali-arrested-in-israel-on-suspicion-of-harassing-policewoman/0000018e-c380-dc93-adce-eff0f9720000</guid></item><item><title>国家检察官称，以色列公司 Cognyte 在未经许可的情况下向缅甸出售网络情报系统</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-company-cognyte-sold-spyware-to-myanmar-without-license-says-state-attorney/0000018e-c2fa-dc93-adce-eefaa19f0000</link><description>《国土报》透露，科格尼特向缅甸出售网络情报系统，违反了全球武器禁运，并且以色列宣布已停止向该国出口武器，但总检察长办公室宣布不会展开调查</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 16:47:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-company-cognyte-sold-spyware-to-myanmar-without-license-says-state-attorney/0000018e-c2fa-dc93-adce-eefaa19f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列交战第 186 天：哈马斯称新的停战提议无法满足其要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-186-hamas-says-new-truce-proposal-doesnt-meet-its-demands/0000018e-c391-d480-a99e-cfd7c5bf0001</link><description>哈马斯表示，最近的人质释放/停火提议未能满足巴勒斯坦各派别的要求 ■ 据《纽约时报》报道，伊朗正在通过中东向约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人走私武器 ■ 沃伦参议员成为第一位表示以色列在加沙的行动可能在法律上构成种族灭绝的美国参议员■ 土耳其将限制对以色列的各种出口，直至宣布加沙停火 ■ 以下是战争爆发 186 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 16:15:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-186-hamas-says-new-truce-proposal-doesnt-meet-its-demands/0000018e-c391-d480-a99e-cfd7c5bf0001</guid></item><item><title>民主党高层不会就即将向以色列出售 F-15 给予拜登橡皮图章，这可能会改变游戏规则</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/potential-game-changer-top-democrat-wont-give-biden-rubber-stamp-on-f-15-sales-to-israel/0000018e-c36d-d1b7-a3af-e76f98460000</link><description>众议院外交事务委员会的首席民主党人宣布，他正在等待拜登就以色列在加沙的行为做出保证，然后才会批准向以色列出售价值 180 亿美元的 F-15 战斗机。他说：“我认为不分青红皂白的轰炸已经够了。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 15:55:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/potential-game-changer-top-democrat-wont-give-biden-rubber-stamp-on-f-15-sales-to-israel/0000018e-c36d-d1b7-a3af-e76f98460000</guid></item><item><title>“证据不足”：德国在国际法院否认协助以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/flimsy-evidence-germany-denies-charge-of-aiding-alleged-israeli-genocide-in-gaza-at-icj/0000018e-c328-d6f4-afaf-ef6aa3890000</link><description>德国的一名法律顾问表示，尼加拉瓜在联合国最高法院的案件很仓促，应该被驳回，因为德国和其他西方国家面临着向以色列出口武器的抗议。德国是以色列最大的武器供应国之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/flimsy-evidence-germany-denies-charge-of-aiding-alleged-israeli-genocide-in-gaza-at-icj/0000018e-c328-d6f4-afaf-ef6aa3890000</guid></item><item><title>德国公司以加沙战争为由拒绝向以色列残奥会提供门球供应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/german-firm-refuses-to-provide-goalball-supply-to-israeli-paralympics-citing-gaza-war/0000018e-c2ec-d6f4-afaf-eeeec0b20000</link><description>德国公司 KSG GmbH 做出这一决定是因为它相信“采取这一立场对于坚持我们的原则和支持和平解决冲突的努力是必要的”</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:20:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/german-firm-refuses-to-provide-goalball-supply-to-israeli-paralympics-citing-gaza-war/0000018e-c2ec-d6f4-afaf-eeeec0b20000</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，本-格维尔的警察局长任命将完成他对以色列警察的接管</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-will-complete-his-takeover-of-the-police-top-officials-say/0000018e-c295-dc93-adce-eef5af430000</link><description>“罪犯第一次任命专员”：以色列警方高层将本-格维尔对警察局长的选择描述为极右翼国家安全部长及其幕僚长（前山顶人物）的“傀儡”和“唯唯诺诺的人”青年活动家</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 14:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-police-chief-pick-will-complete-his-takeover-of-the-police-top-officials-say/0000018e-c295-dc93-adce-eef5af430000</guid></item></channel></rss>